    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Validation results demonstrate strong aggregate agreement between CFD predictions and in-vitro measurements (RMSE = 0.0031 g/100 L, R^2 = 0.94, r = 0.97), providing high confidence in model fidelity across the operating envelope. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2. The credibility assessment team concludes that the CFD model is sufficiently credible for its intended use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
